      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(1 comment)\n\n> sanity-sec is the only other test suite that uses fs_log_size and\n > is not tested by this patch. We should add this test suite to make\n > sure the changes to fs_log_size didn't break anything.\n\nIt's very unlikely, since increasing fs_log_size is only going to detect fewer actual regressions, rather than causing more test failures, but I'm OK if you want to add it.\n\nJames N, I'd be grateful if you could refresh the patch per your comments.",
